OL,3,CSuspected historic munition discovered
OL,4,Cin Bangor
OL,6,FA security operation is underway in Co
OL,7,FDown following the discovery of
OL,8,Fsuspected historic munition.
OL,10,FMembers of the public have been asked
OL,11,Fto avoid the Ward Park area of Bangor
OL,12,Fduring the operation on Friday evening.
OL,14,FA police spokesperson said officers
OL,15,Fare working to assess the object.
OL,17,F"We appreciate this may cause some
OL,18,Fdisruption, however keeping people
OL,19,Fsafe is paramount and we will not take
OL,20,Fany risks," they said.
